{"tid":2346402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"海賊王作者支持台獨？中國粉看「2個國旗並列」崩潰求解釋","createTime":"2020-12-30T08:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T09:06:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d714cb9478c651d73c5a7ae5a36b0fc73660946","tid":2346402,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:32:21.000Z","msg":"日本人氣漫畫「One Piece」《海賊王》（航海王）紅遍全球，連載超過20年，吸引了成千上萬的粉絲追捧。除了日本之外，也在30多個國家、地區發行，一直是出版社人氣最高的漫畫。但今（30）日，作者尾田榮一郎卻遭到中國網友抨擊他「立場有問題」，要求他做出說明並公開道歉，原因則是他所繪彩頁上同時出現了中國跟台灣國旗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/02/2752526-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F02%2F2752526-PH.jpg&h=1968122d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ▲魯夫銅像。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n近日中國網友突然挖出尾田榮一郎2015年，海賊王第790話的彩頁，指出上面飄揚的台灣國旗跟不遠處的中國五星旗，認為作者將台灣跟中國國旗並列，等於支持台灣跟中國是平等國家，不少網友看到都崩潰表示：「尾田夾帶私貨！房子塌了」、「這到底怎麼回事，不希望海賊王跟分裂國家有關」、「希望得到一個解釋」、「坐等尾田道歉，出版社發聲明」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/30/2961360-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F30%2F2961360-PH.jpg&h=dff5af6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼尾田榮一郎5年前彩頁被質疑承認台灣是國家。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/30/2961361-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F30%2F2961361-PH.jpg&h=1e7b70aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但也有海賊粉絲指出，這是尾田榮一郎在漫畫銷量破世界紀錄時，為了感謝各地區發行商所繪製的彩頁，由於海賊王中文版在2015年主要還是以台灣出版社為主，因此畫上代表台灣旗幟，認為這並不能代表什麼政治立場，「外國人沒有我們這種意識，想太多給自己找罪受」、「這都是4、5年前的圖，為什麼現在突然拿出來批判？」也有網友認為可以要求作者公開道歉：「順便向世界宣傳一個中國。」兩方人馬對戰，吵得不可開交。"},{"pid":"f57f4f1bf21562501b453e86fe90c9777bf83fc8","tid":2346402,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"OP世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64980b95f6e322779171eb7779acc1f2c255ec5f","tid":2346402,"uid":56806,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"芝麻人不願接受現實 <br />\n台灣同你地中國就係兩個唔同嘅國家<br />\n仲有將來香港都係"},{"pid":"57734a160f37c012f7ce57613b61e94fba1de17e","tid":2346402,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f57f4f1bf21562501b453e86fe90c9777bf83fc8","tid":2346402,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"OP世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8a7f02f3dce054ca7f18615d9a4abc4a63c8b9","tid":2346402,"uid":232229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"又要召喚蘇辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012515888a16546eec96de02e5706470c3f92905","tid":2346402,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"建議取消五星旗，以符合一個中國（中華民國）原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c073794213b92a4da8a6049ef99b03131e32bb","tid":2346402,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:37:03.000Z","msg":"又要道歉<br />\n返屋企吔蕉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74ac03b548593af696f931d5b6fe37ac4b8a19b","tid":2346402,"uid":222238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64980b95f6e322779171eb7779acc1f2c255ec5f","tid":2346402,"uid":56806,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"芝麻人不願接受現實 <br />\n台灣同你地中國就係兩個唔同嘅國家<br />\n仲有將來香港都係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"新彊, 西藏, 南蒙古都係"},{"pid":"c8da8baa18e43bd06a59efdf233c8ee738db6944","tid":2346402,"uid":220942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:43:55.000Z","msg":"咁就要睇下中國為OP帶來幾多收益喇<img src=\"/assets/